242412048625554645.Text: Synnolian Tunifus needs five units of willow anther for cure paralyzation potions. He admitted he steals willow anther from the flowers growing around the house of Gurak gro-Bagrat. His house is on the mainland, just north of the Foreign Quarter.

25446804913335114.Text: I told Synnolian Tunifus I would not be able to bring him the five units of willow anther he asked for. He was disappointed, and told me to take a day to reflect on my shortcomings, and attempt to amend them before I approach him again for a lay healer mission.

175427632321622617.Text: I delivered five units of willow anther to Synnolian Tunifus. He gave me a cure paralyzation potion and a valuable book as a reward.
